283
00:23:18,090 --> 00:23:19,390
So...

284
00:23:22,390 --> 00:23:24,100
let's have a date tomorrow.

285
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:28,260
What?

286
00:23:30,130 --> 00:23:33,940
A real date, just the two of us.

287
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:43,660
<i>Is making good memories before death
a good enough reason?</i>

288
00:23:45,435 --> 00:23:47,580
Where did you want to take me?

289
00:23:47,580 --> 00:23:49,135
My special place.

290
00:23:49,135 --> 00:23:52,205
Thank you for being born.

291
00:23:53,710 --> 00:23:56,640
You saved my life too.

292
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:58,860
You're the only one I love.
